- Times previously contacted: {{ $json.timesChased }}

This is a {{ $json.urgency }}. {{ $json.timesChased === 0 ? 'This is the first contact.' : `We have contacted them ${$json.timesChased} time(s) before.` }}

End with a call to action to pay immediately or get in touch to discuss.

